Marka loo eego fahamka nidaamyada sharciga ugu da'da weyn, kaliya haweenkii Muxammad ayaa ahaa kuwa la faray inay xijaab ka dhigtaan aayadda (33:59), midkoodna ma lahayn wax shuruud ah oo haweenka si ay u daboolaan. <ref name="Glassé 1989 413">{{Cite book|title=The Concise Encyclopaedia of Islam|publisher=Stacey International|year=1989|location=London, England|page=413}}</ref>  Iyadoo ay taasi jirto, dhammaan dugsiyada [[Shariicada|shareecada]] ee diinta ayaa amar ku bixiyay in qaybaha jidhka, gaar ahaan qoorta, anqawyada, iyo suxullada hoostooda, lagu daboolo dadweynaha.<ref name="Glassé 1989 413" /> Qaar ka mid [[Shariicada|ah nidaamyada sharciga ayaa]] u arka xijaabka inuu yahay dhar daboolaya wax kasta oo aan ahayn wejiga iyo gacmaha, <ref>Fisher, Mary Pat. ''Living Religions''. New Jersey: Pearson Education, 2008.</ref> halka qaar kalena ay u arkaan amar daboolaya jirka oo dhan, oo ay ku jiraan wejiga iyo gacmaha.  Haweenka [[Iiraan|Iran]] iyo [[Afgaanistan|Afgaanistaan]] waxaa looga baahan yahay sharcigu inay xirtaan indho-shareerka.  Iyadoo xeerka ciqaabta [[Iiraan|la soo saaray]] 1983-kii, dumarkii ku xad-gudbay xeerarka xijaabka waxaa lagu xukumay "74 jeedal" (Iran).<ref>Sanam Vakil: ''[https://books.google.se/books?id=WB3m-cBtrQ4C&pg=PA67&dq=ataturk+veils&hl=sv&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj9vpn3m7TzAhXKxIsKHVjRC40Q6AF6BAgIEAI#v=onepage&q=ataturk%20veils&f=false Women and Politics in the Islamic Republic of Iran: Action and Reaction] {{Webarchive}}''</ref>

Qaar ka mid ah dalalka Yurub iyo dunida Muslimka ayaa soo saaray sharciyo mamnuucaya in meelaha qaarkood lagu xiro indho-shareerka. Haweenka ku nool meelo kala duwan oo adduunka ah ayaa sidoo kale la saaray cadaadis aan rasmi ahayn si ay u daboolaan. Ma aha wax sharci ah oo looga baahan yahay [[Sacuudi Carabiya]], laakiin dhaxal sugaha Boqortooyada Mohammed bin Salman ayaa sheegay in haweenku ay weli ku qasban yihiin inay xirtaan "dhar wanaagsan oo ixtiraam leh".      Jihaad doonka Falastiiniyiinta ee xiriirka la leh Hoggaanka United ( UNLU ) ee Gaza ayaa diiday siyaasadda indho-shareerka dumarka lagu soo rogo.  Waddamada Islaamka qaarkood ee lagu dhaqmo [[Shariicada|axkaamta shareecada]], haweenka waxaa laga ilaaliyaa inay ka qayb qaataan nolosha bulshada iyagoon la socon qaraabo lab ah oo ku jira qaabka xijaabka iyo axkaamta xijaabka  iyo inay keligood safraan. 

Maanta , ururada argagixisada ah ee asaasiga ah oo si adag uga soo horjeeda waxbarashada haweenka iyo ka qaybgalka nolosha bulshada ee qaabka fahamka xijaabka ayaa sii wada jiritaankooda caalamka Islaamka waxayna abaabulaan weeraro ka dhan ah xarumaha waxbarashada iyo gaar ahaan ardayda gabdhaha ah. (Fiiri. [[Daliban|Daalibaan]], Boko Haram, Malala Yousafzai )
